---
// Research component
---

<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-4 font-serif">Our Research Focus</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We conduct cutting-edge research in biorehabilitation, combining engineering expertise
        with clinical insights to develop innovative solutions for neurological disorders.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Research Areas -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif mr-4">01</span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 font-serif">Neurorehabilitation Tools</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Development of advanced technologies and methodologies for assessment and treatment
          of neurological disorders, focusing on stroke rehabilitation, spinal cord injury,
          and neurodegenerative diseases.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Robotic-assisted rehabilitation systems
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Virtual reality therapy platforms
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Wearable gait analysis systems
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif mr-4">02</span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 font-serif">Engineering Expertise</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Leveraging multidisciplinary engineering approaches to solve complex biomedical challenges
          through innovative design, signal processing, and mechatronic systems.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Mechatronic system design
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Biomedical signal processing
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Control systems and robotics
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Research Areas Grid -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 text-center mb-8 font-serif">Key Research Areas</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif">01</span>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 mt-1 font-serif">Gait Analysis</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Advanced biomechanical analysis for movement assessment and rehabilitation</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif">02</span>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 mt-1 font-serif">EMG Processing</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Electromyography signal analysis for muscle activation studies</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif">03</span>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 mt-1 font-serif">Adaptive Control</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Intelligent control systems for rehabilitation robotics</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif">04</span>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 mt-1 font-serif">Stroke Recovery</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Technologies for post-stroke motor function recovery</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif">05</span>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 mt-1 font-serif">Wearable Tech</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Portable devices for continuous monitoring and therapy</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-navy-700 p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-700 font-serif">06</span>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 mt-1 font-serif">Clinical Validation</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Evidence-based research through clinical trials and studies</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Funding Section -->
    <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 text-center mb-8 font-serif">Research Funding &amp; Support</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 font-serif">Government Grants</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Supported by DST, DBT, and other national funding agencies</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 font-serif">Industry Partners</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Collaborative projects with healthcare and technology companies</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2 font-serif">International Collaborations</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Global research partnerships and exchange programs</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
